OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781750865
OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FAround 200 lives have been saved
OL,7,Fthanks to a vaccine against cervical
OL,8,Fcancer, with that figure set to rise
OL,9,Fas people age and more are vaccinated,
OL,10,Fdata from England suggests.
OL,12,FA study funded by Cancer Research UK
OL,13,Fand led by Queen Mary University of
OL,14,FLondon shows the human papillomavirus
OL,15,F(HPV) vaccine is working to help wipe
OL,16,Fout cervical cancer across the country.
OL,18,FThe study estimated that children
OL,19,Fvaccinated at age 12`13 have close to
OL,20,Fzero risk of dying from cervical
OL,21,Fcancer before the age of 30.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
