OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781750865
OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FBetween 2020 and 2024, there were no
OL,7,Fdeaths from cervical cancer in women
OL,8,Faged 20 to 24 in England for the first
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FThe study, published in The Lancet
OL,12,Fmedical journal, also found that from
OL,13,F2015-19 there was an 80% reduction in
OL,14,Fcervical cancer deaths among women
OL,15,Faged 20-24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
