PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781750865
OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FProfessor Peter Sasieni, lead author
OL,7,Ffrom Queen Mary, said: "We estimate
OL,8,Fthat since its introduction, HPV
OL,9,Fvaccination has prevented nearly 200
OL,10,Fyoung women from dying from cervical
OL,11,Fcancer in England.
OL,13,F"But that's just the tip of the
OL,14,Ficeberg ` as vaccinated generations
OL,15,Fgrow older, we'll see many more lives
OL,16,Fsaved from cervical cancer."
OL,18,FThe jab was introduced for girls in
OL,19,F2008 and for boys in 2019. Boys are
OL,20,Fgiven the vaccine to protect against
OL,21,Fseveral other types of cancer.
