OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FHPV refers to a group of viruses which
OL,7,Fcan be transmitted through sexual
OL,8,Fcontact and cause no symptoms.
OL,10,FAround 13 high-risk types of HPV are
OL,11,Fknown to cause 99.7% of cervical
OL,12,Fcancers.
OL,14,FHowever, despite progress towards
OL,15,Feliminating cervical cancer, experts
OL,16,Fare worried about falling vaccination
OL,17,Frates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
