OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781750865
OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FThe HPV vaccine is routinely offered
OL,7,Fin Year 8, with some local authorities
OL,8,Frunning catch-up programmes in year 9
OL,9,Fand 10.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FIn England from 2024-2025, 71.7% of
OL,17,Fgirls were vaccinated in Year 8 as
OL,18,Fwere 67% of boys.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
