CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781750865
OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FBy Year 10, this reached 75.5% in
OL,7,Fgirls and 70.5% in boys, but it was
OL,8,Fbelow the World Health Organisation
OL,9,Ftarget of 90% for girls and lower than
OL,10,Fthe previous year.
OL,12,FLondon had the lowest HPV vaccination
OL,13,Frates at 62.6% for girls and 57.7% for
OL,14,Fboys.
OL,16,FCancer Research UK said a fall in jab
OL,17,Fuptake threatens progress, with around
OL,18,Fone in four young people currently
OL,19,Fleaving school unprotected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
