PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781750865
OL,3,CAround 200 lives saved in England from
OL,4,Ccervical cancer due to HPV jab
OL,6,FNHS director of vaccination, Caroline
OL,7,FTemmink, said: "This hugely
OL,8,Fencouraging news shows the life-saving
OL,9,Fimpact of the HPV vaccine and it's
OL,10,Fincredibly exciting to be able to say
OL,11,Fto this whole generation: cervical
OL,12,Fcancer and some other cancers
OL,13,Fshouldn't be a risk for you."
